T1  - Systemic chemokine levels, coronary heart disease, and ischemic stroke events: The PRIME study
A1  - Canoui-Poitrine F.
A1  - Luc G.
A1  - Mallat Z.
A1  - Machez E.
A1  - Bingham A.
A1  - Ferrieres J.
